Our Reichsbanner can try to mimic the paramilitary organization and training of the Austrian Republikanischer Schutzbund (Republican Protection Units), the paramilitary branch of the Austrian social democrats, but we don't expect much success.

[? if austrian_parliament_seen and not austrian_civil_war_seen: We are also helping the Austrian Social Democratic Worker's Party build up their resources in preparation for a future struggle, legally and illegally. The irony of doing this while historically opposing the same struggle in our own country is lost on us. ?]


